OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few early showers possible
OL,6,Facross the eastern Borders, otherwise
OL,7,Fa dry day with variable amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud and some sunny intervals. Winds
OL,9,Fbecoming light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome sunshine at first, but gradually
OL,13,Fclouding over from the west. Cloud and
OL,14,Frain will spread east to all parts
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FRain will soon clear east
OL,18,Fthen sunny spells and showers. Drier
OL,19,Ffor a time in the afternoon before
OL,20,Ffurther showers later, heavy at times.
OL,21,FCool and blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
